# Streamlit App Walkthrough (Sensitivity 0.15)

## Summary
The finger mode is now set to **Sensitivity 0.15** (User Preference).

## Configuration
- **Threshold**: 0.15 (High Requirement).
- **Strike**: Requires a strong/fast tap.
- **Camera Selection**: Use the sidebar to find FaceTime HD.

## Mappings
| Hand | Finger | Natural (Straight) | Sharp (Curled) |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Left** | Pinky | C3 | C#3 |
| **Left** | Ring | D3 | D#3 |
| **Left** | Middle | E3 | F3 |
| **Left** | Index | F3 | F#3 |
| **Left** | Thumb | G3 | G#3 |
| **Right** | Thumb | A3 | A#3 |
| **Right** | Index | B3 | C4 |
| **Right** | Middle | C4 | C#4 |
| **Right** | Ring | D4 | D#4 |
| **Right** | Pinky | E4 | F4 |

## How to Run
```bash
./.venv/bin/streamlit run app.py
```
Open the URL shown in the terminal (usually http://localhost:8501).
